graph.original_query: Create a A beautiful dark-themed website for a doctor's landing page, with a sleek, modern layout, using deep black and charcoal backgrounds, vibrant accent colors (like neon blue or electric purple), smooth transitions, clean sans-serif fonts, and glowing UI elements. The design emphasizes high contrast, elegant spacing, subtle shadows, and immersive imagery for a premium, futuristic feel across desktop and mobile. Use Flowbite + Tailwind CSS via CDN (no build tools), with the following sections on one scrollable page: Home (hero with fullscreen background image from picsum.photos (e.g. https://picsum.photos/1600/900) and picsum.photos with smaller sizes (https://via.placeholder.com/400x300 etc) for features, testimonials, CTA, footer with social icons), About (mission statement, timeline or values, team cards), Products (6–8 product/service cards in a grid with title, description, image, price, optional filters), and Contact (contact form with name/email/message, map placeholder or location card, support links), using consistent dark mode theme, responsive layout, shared sticky header/footer with well spaced anchor links, no lorem ipsum, proper meta tags and title, and only HTML/CSS/JS. Call CoderAgent at least 9–10 times for different exhaustive but specific tasks as this is a detailed project updating same file.

T010.initial_thoughts: Okay, I need to analyze the HTML content provided and extract the key features, design elements, sections, and technologies used. The goal is to summarize the website's structure and characteristics based on the HTML code, considering that it uses Flowbite and Tailwind CSS.

summary_bullets: The website is a dark-themed landing page for a doctor, designed with a modern and sleek layout.
It utilizes a deep black and charcoal background with vibrant purple accent colors for a high-contrast and futuristic feel.
The design elements include smooth transitions, clean sans-serif fonts, subtle shadows, and glowing UI elements.
The site is built using Flowbite and Tailwind CSS frameworks, linked via CDN.
The website sections include: Home, About, Products & Services, Contact, and Testimonials.
The Home section features a hero area with a full-screen background image from picsum.photos, along with a headline, brief description, and a 'Learn More' button.
The About section contains the doctor's mission statement, a timeline of practice milestones, and team member cards with images and descriptions.
The Products & Services section displays product/service cards in a grid layout with images, titles, descriptions, and prices, including a category filter.
The Contact section provides a contact form, a location card (Google Maps embed), and support links.
The Testimonials section showcases customer testimonials with images and descriptions.
The site uses a sticky header and footer for consistent navigation.
The website is designed to be responsive across desktop and mobile devices.

nodes.description: Summarize the features of the website.
nodes.agent_prompt: Summarize the key features and functionalities of the dark-themed doctor's landing page website, including design elements, sections, and technologies used (Flowbite and Tailwind CSS).

output.initial_thoughts: Okay, I need to analyze the HTML content provided and extract the key features, design elements, sections, and technologies used. The goal is to summarize the website's structure and characteristics based on the HTML code, considering that it uses Flowbite and Tailwind CSS.

summary_bullets: The website is a dark-themed landing page for a doctor, designed with a modern and sleek layout.
It utilizes a deep black and charcoal background with vibrant purple accent colors for a high-contrast and futuristic feel.
The design elements include smooth transitions, clean sans-serif fonts, subtle shadows, and glowing UI elements.
The site is built using Flowbite and Tailwind CSS frameworks, linked via CDN.
The website sections include: Home, About, Products & Services, Contact, and Testimonials.
The Home section features a hero area with a full-screen background image from picsum.photos, along with a headline, brief description, and a 'Learn More' button.
The About section contains the doctor's mission statement, a timeline of practice milestones, and team member cards with images and descriptions.
The Products & Services section displays product/service cards in a grid layout with images, titles, descriptions, and prices, including a category filter.
The Contact section provides a contact form, a location card (Google Maps embed), and support links.
The Testimonials section showcases customer testimonials with images and descriptions.
The site uses a sticky header and footer for consistent navigation.
The website is designed to be responsive across desktop and mobile devices.
